    "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nSpark-3.4  updates the requirement of `lineSep` accepting 1 or 2 characters in `CSVOptions`.\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\n\r\nWe need to update the compatibility doc to explicitly mention that 2 characters lineSep is not supported on GPU.\r\n\r\n```\r\n   // see GpuCSVScan.scala\r\n    if (parsedOptions.lineSeparator.getOrElse(\"\\n\") != \"\\n\") {\r\n      meta.willNotWorkOnGpu(\"GpuCSVScan only supports \\\"\\\\n\\\" as a line separator\")\r\n    }\r\n```\r\n**Additional context**\r\n\r\nPR commit: https://github.com/apache/spark/commit/bb4c477871",
